		"description": "<p><em><strong>Association:</strong> Ranger class</em></p><p>One of the best ways to rid yourself of enemies is to turn them into friends.</p><p>Until the spell ends, you gain an expertise die on Culture and Persuasion checks involving your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.t7ujv9cc4us40fj9]{Studied Adversary}.&nbsp;</p><p>Additionally, when you restore hit points to a Studied Adversary, you may reroll any die result of 1 that comes up when determining the amount of hit points restored. You must use the new roll.</p>",
